										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>NIH (including help desks) will be closed on Monday, May 29, 2023 for the federal holiday (Memorial Day). If a grant application due date falls on a <a href="https://www.opm.gov/policy-data-oversight/pay-leave/federal-holidays/#url=2023">federal holiday</a>, the application deadline is automatically extended to the next business day.</p>
